  "title": "How to Understand Differences in Sales Reports",
  "slug": "how-to-view-and-customize-your-superpos-sales-repo",
  "description": "<p>QPOS merchants who are confused by different numbers in their reports, need to combine online and offline sales data, or want to fix tallying errors.</p>",
