      "id": 121,
      "question_id": 121,
      "step_order": 1,
      "step_title": "Overview",
      "content": "<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">This guide explains why your daily sales report doesn&#39;t match your transaction logs (usually due to refunds or cancellations) and shows you exactly how to find and fix them using your QPOS BackOffice and a simple spreadsheet.</span></p>",
      "image_url": null,
      "video_url": null,
      "block_type": "step",
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "id": 409,
      "question_id": 121,
      "step_order": 2,
      "step_title": "Before You Begin",
      "content": "<ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Access to your QPOS BackOffice.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">A computer with spreadsheet software (e.g., Microsoft Excel, Google Sheets, Apple Numbers) for analyzing exported CSV files.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Understanding of your store&#39;s transaction types (offline, online, refunds, cancellations).</span></li></ul>",
      "image_url": null,
      "video_url": null,
      "block_type": "step",
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "id": 410,
      "question_id": 121,
      "step_order": 3,
      "step_title": "Understanding Offline vs. Online Sales",
      "content": "<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">It&#39;s important to know the difference between offline and online transactions when reviewing your reports.</span></p><ul><li><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Offline Transactions:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\"> These are orders made directly at your Point of Sale (POS) device, regardless of internet connection. Examples include dine-in or take-away orders paid at the counter.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Online Transactions:</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\"> These orders are placed through integrated platforms like Beep Delivery, QR Order &amp; Pay, your Webstore, or third-party platforms (e.g., Foodpanda).</span></li></ul>",
      "image_url": null,
      "video_url": null,
      "block_type": "step",
      "images": []
    },
